'''''Gurth an Glamhoth!''''' is a [[Sindarin]] phrase muttered by [[Tuor]] when he and [[Voronwë]] spotted an [[Orc]] encampment and he was tempted to attack them and take their meat.<ref>{{UT|Tuor}}, p. 39</ref> It translates as "Death to the [[Glamhoth]]!"<ref>{{UT|1a}}, note 18</ref>
